                                       Joel: 732-600-4716<br>          
                                   </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="info-box mt-4">
                                    <i class="bx bx-store"></i>
                                    <h3>Partner Stores</h3>
                                    <p><b>Jade's Filipino Restaurant and Groceries</b><br>
                                       6701 Black Horse Pike, Egg Harbor Township, NJ 08234<br>
                                       609-272-2882<br>
                                       

                                       &nbsp;
